Package: jspputils
Type: Package
Title: Series of utilities to interface R with proteomics data analysis
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Sebastian Paez
Maintainer: Sebastian Paez <jspaezp@gmail.com>
Description: Suite of tools to make life easyer ... reading data from the output
    of the commmonly used search engines in the lab, and some util functions to 
    make easyer plots and such .... It installs all my commonly used R packages
    in a convenient way.
